title: Shane Watson Plays Pak Super League
text: Cricket Â· He said that various leading players of the world want to play PSL, so he also joined it and he is waiting for the start of PSL . He plays PSL and proves his abilities and skills to play T20 cricket. The players of various test playing nations and other players of the associate teams are also want to play in PSL, which is going to be played in February in UAE. Karachi, Another superstar will include in Pak Super League . It is the good news for the organizers of T20 event of Pakistan super league. Australian all rounder, Shane Watson has shown his willingness to play Pakistan super league. Now 152 foreign players have joined PSL, in which various leading players of the world are playing. Watson was the member of the Australian team, who won the world cup title for two times. He showed his pleasure to join PSL. Advertisement
